KdCn8kKMN9H5","target":"recfrXyxhuYOczKTm","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recF1KdCn8kKMN9H5","target":"recIJFRcqI6KbKgXb","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recF1KdCn8kKMN9H5","target":"recHAv7LzOUc4wj2r","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recF1KdCn8kKMN9H5","target":"recADz5cMmoTWAEzV","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recF1KdCn8kKMN9H5","target":"recFPceE2ivY1B3sX","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recF1KdCn8kKMN9H5","target":"recdm9AlLF01lFAfP","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recF1KdCn8kKMN9H5","target":"recekTocE5mIkvDEk","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"recG1qMwwJ7fTA8yM","ref":"Hos.9.1","text":"Rejoice not, O Israel, for joy, as other people: for thou hast gone a whoring from thy God, thou hast loved a reward upon every cornfloor.","year":-760},{"id":"recloy4FYi0qIFbqc","ref":"Hos.9.2","text":"The floor and the winepress shall not feed them, and the new wine shall fail in her.","year":-760},{"id":"recv5cNLYcmarVCF2","ref":"Hos.9.3","text":"They shall not dwell in the LORD’S land; but Ephraim shall return to Egypt, and they shall eat unclean things in Assyria.","year":-760},{"id":"recr56FOB7MpOhlwt","ref":"Hos.9.4","text":"They shall not offer wine offerings to the LORD, neither shall they be pleasing unto him: their sacrifices shall be unto them as the bread of mourners; all that eat thereof shall be polluted: for their bread for their soul shall not come into the house of the LORD.","year":-760},{"id":"recp0P6lcLM2kS2Y3","ref":"Hos.9.5","text":"What will ye do in the solemn day, and in the day of the feast of the LORD?","year":-760},{"id":"rec1VvW8Fp0hC6uMw","ref":"Hos.9.6","text":"For, lo, they are gone because of destruction: Egypt shall gather them up, Memphis shall bury them: the pleasant places for their silver, nettles shall possess them: thorns shall be in their tabernacles.","year":-760},{"id":"recgPbSUgRDzL5kD2","ref":"Hos.9.7","text":"The days of visitation are come, the days of recompence are come; Israel shall know it: the prophet is a fool, the spiritual man is mad, for the multitude of thine iniquity, and the great hatred.","year":-760},{"id":"recKZl7nRxza379rY","ref":"Hos.9.8","text":"The watchman of Ephraim was with my God: but the prophet is a snare of a fowler in all his ways, and hatred in the house of his God.","year":-760}]}
